'''Allynic E'Kles's holocron''' was a [[Holocron/Legends|holocron]] made by [[Allynic E'Kles]], a [[Caamasi/Legends|Caamasi]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]]. He stored his [[Jedi investigator/Legends|investigative]] knowledge and many [[Memnis|memnii]] within the holocron, the latter of which could be accessed by [[Telepathy/Legends|telepathic]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].

